&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;还有一个特别优秀的地方：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;画作逼真，生动还原了动物生活的环境和真实情景。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; medium=&quot;&quot; start=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;比如这只飞翔的翼龙，鲜艳的大嘴十分夺目，仿佛下一秒就冲出书页、飞到眼前。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; medium=&quot;&quot; start=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;这是因为，书中的手绘插图，参考的都是“国家地理学会”第一线的摄影作品或研究成果。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; medium=&quot;&quot; start=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;346&quot; data-backw=&quot;578&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5984375&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1280&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OCIwxC35pAjLPl7pw6fbicd7pBZIuu4rpV5MbqMicSVpO5wZP1gyCGuryKTNB7D3WeBVrQWp8kRHxYdzBbt7CN4g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;也有一些摄影作品，可以让你近距离观察那些平时难得一见的神奇动物。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;
